Ranking interactions for consensus using all tools

rank_interactions.Rd

Ranking interactions for consensus using all tools

Usage

rank_interactions(
  cell_type_pair,
  connectome,
  sca,
  cytotalk,
  natmi,
  logfc,
  obj_cell2cell,
  obj_cellchat,
  obj_cpdb
)

Arguments

cell_type_pair

cell type of interest for filtering

connectome

dataframe with connectome results (interactions ordered by descending score)

sca

dataframe with sca results (interactions ordered by descending score)

cytotalk

dataframe with cytotalk results (interactions ordered by descending score)

natmi

dataframe with natmi results (interactions ordered by descending score)

logfc

dataframe with logfc results (interactions ordered by descending score)

obj_cell2cell

dataframe with cell2cell results (interactions ordered by (ascending) p-values)

obj_cellchat

dataframe with cellchat results (interactions ordered by (ascending) p-values)

obj_cpdb

dataframe with cellphonedb results (interactions ordered by (ascending) p-values)
